{"tid":1845930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"先唔好講責任呀道德呀咁遠，風險同人工係咪唔成正比先？","createTime":"2020-01-27T11:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T03:06:39.000Z","uid":40250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5544294c2be1c407c5ef31fbd728484991c4b7","tid":1845930,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:50:35.000Z","msg":"望下班高官，望下班黑警，望下入境同衛生署班柒頭，你地收咁既人工值唔值得冒咁大風險去死先？ <br />\n<br />\n先唔好講乜撚職業道德，咩野醫護責任感d閪野先喇，你係有skill有知識既，到真係outbreak個陣，人地跪係到求你幫拖喇，駛閪依家咁幫左佢仲當老撚馮咁？<br />\n<br />\n真係放唔低香港人，放唔低病人既，就先忍痛一下，反正都要死，收貴幾倍搵番一筆錢俾屋企人先。<br />\n<br />\n如果到時候有班撚樣衝出黎話你趁火打劫乜乜柒柒，咁你地問下自己，呢班閪人值唔值得你咁博。<br />\n<br />\n只要班廢柴高官收少幾個月糧就解決到，又或者慳番海洋公園個一百億，出番呢筆錢有幾難？"},{"pid":"0a0fe3aff439ce288c20f76a30be0a7de1f109d8","tid":1845930,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:53:11.000Z","msg":"明眼人都知唔斷絕病源係政府想殺香港人<br />\n<br />\nObjective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the border.<br />\n&gt; Given Fact: Japan and Macau found #WuhanSARS patients who are from #HKG Airport =&gt; No checking in the departure. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Ro26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=7a64c79a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"84ec40777e1828fa64f54f794725adb07853fe0f","tid":1845930,"